---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="mt-32 border-t border-ink-100 bg-ink-100/40">
  <div class="container-content py-12">
    <div class="grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-[1.4fr_1fr_1fr]">
      <div>
        <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2" aria-label="헤이보카 홈">
          <img src="/images/logo_h.png" alt="헤이보카 로고" width="32" height="32" class="h-8 w-8" />
          <span class="text-lg font-extrabold text-ink-900">
            Hey, <span class="text-primary-600">Voca!</span>
          </span>
        </a>
        <p class="mt-3 max-w-md text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink-700">
          망각 직전 다시 만나는 단어. 게임처럼 즐거운 영어 단어 학습 앱 헤이보카.
        </p>
      </div>

      <nav aria-label="법적 고지" class="text-sm">
        <h2 class="mb-3 font-semibold text-ink-900">법적 고지</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li><a href="/privacy-policy" class="text-ink-700 hover:text-primary-600">개인정보처리방침</a></li>
          <li><a href="/terms-of-service" class="text-ink-700 hover:text-primary-600">서비스 이용약관</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>

      <div class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink-700">
        <h2 class="mb-3 font-semibold text-ink-900">사업자 정보</h2>
        <dl class="space-y-1.5">
          <div class="flex gap-2"><dt class="shrink-0 text-ink-500">상호</dt><dd>슬기로운 사업</dd></div>
          <div class="flex gap-2"><dt class="shrink-0 text-ink-500">대표</dt><dd>조건호</dd></div>
          <div class="flex gap-2"><dt class="shrink-0 text-ink-500">사업자등록번호</dt><dd>315-27-01645</dd></div>
          <div class="flex gap-2"><dt class="shrink-0 text-ink-500">이메일</dt><dd><a href="mailto:ceo@ghmate.com" class="hover:text-primary-600">ceo@ghmate.com</a></dd></div>
          <div class="flex gap-2"><dt class="shrink-0 text-ink-500">주소</dt><dd>부산광역시 부산진구 동천로 116, 3층 오픈오피스 12호</dd></div>
        </dl>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-10 border-t border-ink-200 pt-6 text-xs text-ink-500">
      © {year} 슬기로운 사업. All rights reserved.
    </p>
  </div>
</footer>
